headline: Nvidia, Other Techs Hurt Dow Jones, But These Names Outperformed In Q1
summary: The overseers of the Dow Jones Industrial Average might regret adding Nvidia to the index.  Since it joined the Dow industrials on Nov. 7, Nvidia stock is down nearly 30%.  Nvidia stock is on track for its worst month since September 2022, when it lost nearly 20%, according to Dow Jones Market Data.
